A civilian airline.
那是一架民航客机。

1090
01:28:27,199 --> 01:28:28,579
CIA spine plane.
是中情局的间谍飞机。

1091
01:28:28,700 --> 01:28:30,539
They were warned.Repeat that--
他们被警告过。重复过多次...

1092
01:28:30,639 --> 01:28:31,760
It was a commercial flight.
它是一架商业航机。

1093
01:28:32,760 --> 01:28:37,800
269 people are dead, Anatoly, including one of our congressmen.
269人死亡，阿纳托利，包括一名我们的国会议员。
（苏联驻美国大使）

1094
01:28:37,999 --> 01:28:39,039
George.
乔治。

1095
01:28:39,220 --> 01:28:41,060
You crossed the line.
你们欺人太盛了。

1096
01:28:48,199 --> 01:28:50,680
[MUSIC PLAYING]
[音乐响起]

1097
01:28:50,760 --> 01:28:54,279
Tensions between the Cold War adversaries continue to escalate.
冷战对手之间的紧张局势，继续升级。

1098
01:28:54,760 --> 01:28:57,199
President Reagan called it an act of barbarism.
里根总统称其为野蛮行为。

1099
01:28:57,640 --> 01:29:00,560
NATO forces remain on alert across Europe.
北约部队在欧洲各地，保持警戒状态。

1100
