We have confirmation on this.
我们已经证实了这一点。

1106
01:29:28,299 --> 01:29:29,439
So these are the opposite sides.
这些是对方的。

1107
01:29:29,720 --> 01:29:31,239
That's 18 million American lives.
那是1800万美国人的生命。

1108
01:29:31,500 --> 01:29:32,520
I think we're launching, sir.
我想我们要发射了，长官。

1109
01:29:33,079 --> 01:29:34,119
Prepare for DEFCON1.
进入核战一级戒备。

1110
01:29:34,359 --> 01:29:36,000
I need confirmation.
我需要确认。

1111
01:29:36,600 --> 01:29:40,279
Mr. President, if this is real, we won't have time for confirmation.
总统先生，如果这是真的，我们没时间确认了。

1112
01:29:41,140 --> 01:29:42,159
[MUSIC PLAYING]
[音乐响起]

1113
01:29:44,840 --> 01:29:46,159
We need a decision.
我们需要一个决定。

1114
