（民众伤亡预测）

1115
01:30:48,619 --> 01:30:50,079
They're reporting, sir.
他们在报告，长官。

1116
01:30:50,179 --> 01:30:51,380
They're standing down.
他们暂停了。

1117
01:30:51,639 --> 01:30:52,640
[GROANING]
[舒缓声]

1118
01:30:52,740 --> 01:30:59,239
Looks like a flock of geese triggered a positive radar hit.
看来是一群鹅的到访，触发了平面现象雷达。

1119
01:30:59,619 --> 01:31:00,680
[GROANING]
[哀叹声]

1120
01:31:04,680 --> 01:31:07,840
The Cold War was in full swing.
冷战正在全面展开。

1121
01:31:08,840 --> 01:31:12,159
The Crusader, he knew he had to keep the pressure on us,
那个“白宫圣战士”，他知道，他必须对我们施加压力，
（伤亡预测数据更新）

1122
01:31:12,720 --> 01:31:15,199
but making sure there were no more mistakes.
但要确保不再犯错。

1123
